Cloudcap Mushroom[dnd-info]=A rare, gray-capped mushroom that thrives in damp caves, known for enhancing perception when processed. One mushroom (enough for one extract) costs 2 gp and weighs 3 oz.

Recipe[dnd-list]=Search for cloudcap mushrooms in dark, moist caverns, growing on rocky walls.;Cut the caps cleanly with a knife, leaving the stem to regrow.;Dry the caps in a ventilated bag for 3 days to prevent rot while retaining potency.
